1
00:00:07,680 --> 00:00:09,910
(WANNA ONE GO: Back to Base, Final Episode)

2
00:00:10,180 --> 00:00:11,719
(They drive along the foggy road...)

3
00:00:11,720 --> 00:00:12,879
(and arrive at another Wanna List location.)

4
00:00:12,880 --> 00:00:14,249
We're here.

5
00:00:14,250 --> 00:00:15,349
We've arrived.

6
00:00:15,350 --> 00:00:17,390
It's so foggy today.

7
00:00:18,160 --> 00:00:19,959
(Where is this foggy place with the mysterious atmosphere?)

8
00:00:19,960 --> 00:00:22,530
They want to see us have fun at a vacation rental.

9
00:00:23,600 --> 00:00:24,600
There are...

10
00:00:24,800 --> 00:00:26,769
jokgu and campfire facilities.

11
00:00:26,770 --> 00:00:27,830
(Campfire)

12
00:00:27,970 --> 00:00:29,700
- Let's go. - Let's get going.

13
00:00:30,270 --> 00:00:31,939
Why does this place look so spooky?

14
00:00:31,940 --> 00:00:32,969
- This is fog, right? - A mountain spirit might come out.

15
00:00:32,970 --> 00:00:34,670
I know. I feel like a mountain spirit might come out.

16
00:00:34,810 --> 00:00:36,609
Is jokgu a good idea?

17
00:00:36,610 --> 00:00:37,610
(Is jokgu a good idea?)

18
00:00:37,740 --> 00:00:39,010
(It's true that the weather is bad.)

19
00:00:39,110 --> 00:00:40,779
They won't be able to beat those who have served in the military.

20
00:00:40,780 --> 00:00:41,879
- That's right. - They won't be a match for us.

21
00:00:41,880 --> 00:00:43,679
(Stop with the military talk.)

22
00:00:43,680 --> 00:00:46,149
They won't be able to beat us. We played jokgu all the time.

23
00:00:46,150 --> 00:00:48,350
I placed first in jokgu in my unit.

24
00:00:48,590 --> 00:00:49,749
Go back into the military.

25
00:00:49,750 --> 00:00:50,990
(Chirpy Birdie List: I want them to redo their military service!)

26
00:00:51,260 --> 00:00:52,789
- I think it's this one. - Is this it?

27
00:00:52,790 --> 00:00:54,159
It's nice.

28
00:00:54,160 --> 00:00:55,929
Gosh, I've always wanted to live in a house with a front yard.

29
00:00:55,930 --> 00:00:56,930
Same here.

30
00:00:56,930 --> 00:00:57,930
(Oh, my!)

31
00:00:57,931 --> 00:00:59,330
Open the door!

32
00:00:59,430 --> 00:01:00,670
Open the door!

33
00:01:00,900 --> 00:01:02,769
- My goodness. - Hey, this place is nice.

34
00:01:02,770 --> 00:01:03,770
This place is really nice.

35
00:01:04,240 --> 00:01:05,669
It's nicer than I expected.

36
00:01:05,670 --> 00:01:06,809
(A cozy place that'll take care of Wanna One's rest)

37
00:01:06,810 --> 00:01:09,370
The stairs remind me of our old dormitory.

38
00:01:09,810 --> 00:01:12,110
(It has the same layout as Wanna One's first dormitory.)

39
00:01:12,280 --> 00:01:13,910
(Let's go and make fun memories today as well.)

40
00:01:14,210 --> 00:01:15,609
When you go to a vacation rental,

41
00:01:15,610 --> 00:01:17,519
you usually have a barbecue or play jokgu.

42
00:01:17,520 --> 00:01:18,679
I looked inside the fridge.

43
00:01:18,680 --> 00:01:20,719
It's completely empty.

44
00:01:20,720 --> 00:01:22,049
- Do we need to shop for groceries? - You're right.

45
00:01:22,050 --> 00:01:23,689
Do we need to shop for groceries using the money from earlier?

46
00:01:23,690 --> 00:01:26,189
- That money is ours. - How about the rest?

47
00:01:26,190 --> 00:01:27,859
- It's ours. - How about the rest?

48
00:01:27,860 --> 00:01:30,899
I don't think it's any business of yours, Min Hyun.

49
00:01:30,900 --> 00:01:32,030
(Jjaeni feels dejected as well.)

50
00:01:32,160 --> 00:01:33,229
What should we do now?

51
00:01:33,230 --> 00:01:34,599
Let's rest briefly and...

52
00:01:34,600 --> 00:01:35,700
Rest again?

53
00:01:36,030 --> 00:01:37,069
We rested in the van.

54
00:01:37,070 --> 00:01:38,499
I charged my energy in the van.

55
00:01:38,500 --> 00:01:39,769
But Sung Woon didn't.

56
00:01:39,770 --> 00:01:41,409
It's okay. My energy gets charged naturally...

57
00:01:41,410 --> 00:01:42,610
when I'm with you guys.

58
00:01:42,970 --> 00:01:44,910
Sung Woon, seriously. You move my heart.

59
00:01:45,510 --> 00:01:47,049
- Let's play jokgu. - Okay.

60
00:01:47,050 --> 00:01:48,050
That sounds good.

61
00:01:48,850 --> 00:01:49,850
Let's go!

62
00:01:49,851 --> 00:01:51,719
- Let's do this! - Let's do this!

63
00:01:51,720 --> 00:01:52,720
(Wanna One sets out to enjoy the vacation rental.)

64
00:01:52,980 --> 00:01:54,389
It's cool and nice.

65
00:01:54,390 --> 00:01:57,119
Hey, using a sun stick is a must when the weather is like this.

66
00:01:57,120 --> 00:01:58,559
You get more tanned...

67
00:01:58,560 --> 00:01:59,860
- when the sun is hiding. - You're right.

68
00:02:00,060 --> 00:02:01,259
- You need to apply it... - Yes.

69
00:02:01,260 --> 00:02:02,459
- on your neck and hands. - I'll apply it.

70
00:02:02,460 --> 00:02:04,829
I can't even feel that I'm wearing something.

71
00:02:04,830 --> 00:02:06,200
Yes, it's very light.

72
00:02:06,970 --> 00:02:09,270
- That's the jokgu field. - It's grass.

73
00:02:09,970 --> 00:02:11,539
Hey, the jokgu field is in great condition.

74
00:02:11,540 --> 00:02:12,939
You don't usually play jokgu.

75
00:02:12,940 --> 00:02:14,440
How would you know anything about the condition of the field?

76
00:02:14,470 --> 00:02:15,840
(Annoyed)

77
00:02:15,940 --> 00:02:18,009
- Will you throw your shoe? - I won't do this.

78
00:02:18,010 --> 00:02:19,940
- My goodness. - Woo Jin annoyed me.

79
00:02:20,680 --> 00:02:21,979
(Dividing up into teams for jokgu)

80
00:02:21,980 --> 00:02:23,880
- Gather around. - Raise your hand if you're good.

81
00:02:23,980 --> 00:02:25,450
(Min Hyun, Jin Young, and Jae Hwan)

82
00:02:25,880 --> 00:02:26,890
(Me)

83
00:02:27,090 --> 00:02:28,619
What's up with the two of you?

84
00:02:28,620 --> 00:02:29,789
Jae Hwan,

85
00:02:29,790 --> 00:02:30,919
- I have a favor to ask. - What is it?

86
00:02:30,920 --> 00:02:32,319
Please don't judge us with your prejudices.

87
00:02:32,320 --> 00:02:35,429
Min Hyun, the two of you can't be good at ball sports.

88
00:02:35,430 --> 00:02:37,559
The two of you can't be good at ball sports.

89
00:02:37,560 --> 00:02:38,629
Hey.

90
00:02:38,630 --> 00:02:39,930
Hey. There he goes.

91
00:02:40,430 --> 00:02:41,670
Hey. There he goes.

92
00:02:42,770 --> 00:02:44,739
- His form was off. - Didn't it look like a dance?

93
00:02:44,740 --> 00:02:46,199
Wasn't that taekkyeon?

94
00:02:46,200 --> 00:02:47,409
I know how to do it.

95
00:02:47,410 --> 00:02:48,410
You look sloppy.

96
00:02:48,410 --> 00:02:49,410
(Referee Chirpy Birdie enters.)

97
00:02:49,411 --> 00:02:50,439
This is how you make it fun.

98
00:02:50,440 --> 00:02:52,779
These two guys who are good with balls...

99
00:02:52,780 --> 00:02:54,109
- are the captains. - Okay.

100
00:02:54,110 --> 00:02:55,149
Play rock-paper-scissors and pick your teammates.

101
00:02:55,150 --> 00:02:56,179
- Shall we pick them? - Yes.

102
00:02:56,180 --> 00:02:57,819
But everyone is equally bad.

103
00:02:57,820 --> 00:02:59,850
- Jae Hwan! - Everyone is equally bad.

104
00:03:00,080 --> 00:03:01,349
Play rock-paper-scissors.

105
00:03:01,350 --> 00:03:02,890
- Rock-paper-scissors! - Rock-paper-scissors! Nice!

106
00:03:03,760 --> 00:03:05,219
Which member will Sung Woon pick first?

107
00:03:05,220 --> 00:03:07,289
- I'm sure it'll be me. - It'll be me.

108
00:03:07,290 --> 00:03:08,889
- I'm a dark horse. - It's me

109
00:03:08,890 --> 00:03:09,959
It's me

110
00:03:09,960 --> 00:03:11,099
You've seen me shoot, right?

111
00:03:11,100 --> 00:03:12,359
I'm pretty good at everything.

112
00:03:12,360 --> 00:03:14,769
You don't know anything about my jokgu skills. I might be good.

113
00:03:14,770 --> 00:03:17,370
Since the ball is round, it's hard to tell who will be good at it.

114
00:03:17,970 --> 00:03:20,369
I know exactly which member has the best jokgu skills.

115
00:03:20,370 --> 00:03:21,939
- I'm good with balls. - You've seen me shoot, right?

116
00:03:21,940 --> 00:03:23,679
You've seen my jokgu form, right?

117
00:03:23,680 --> 00:03:25,239
You've seen my jokgu form, right?

118
00:03:25,240 --> 00:03:27,080
- I'm pretty good at everything. - Wasn't that jegichagi?

119
00:03:27,480 --> 00:03:29,979
(He placed last in the boxing game contest.)

120
00:03:29,980 --> 00:03:31,519
(He placed last in the hammer game contest.)

121
00:03:31,520 --> 00:03:33,020
(He only got made fun of in the past days.)

122
00:03:33,520 --> 00:03:35,650
(Will he finally overcome the sorrowful past?)

123
00:03:35,850 --> 00:03:37,520
Jin Young!

124
00:03:37,960 --> 00:03:40,459
(Team Sung Woon's first member is Jin Young!)

125
00:03:40,460 --> 00:03:42,389
- It goes without saying. - Min Hyun was happy for a second.

126
00:03:42,390 --> 00:03:43,529
It goes without saying.

127
00:03:43,530 --> 00:03:45,059
- You thought it was you, right? - Why did you fool me?

128
00:03:45,060 --> 00:03:47,730
You fooled me last time.

129
00:03:49,200 --> 00:03:50,569
(When they filmed "WANNA ONE GO" in LA 9 years ago,)

130
00:03:50,570 --> 00:03:52,539
(Min Hyun picked a member for the photo mission.)

131
00:03:52,540 --> 00:03:53,540
(Woo Jin, Sung Woon)

132
00:03:54,510 --> 00:03:56,669
(Sung Woon got fooled by Woo Jin.)

133
00:03:56,670 --> 00:03:58,440
(I'm so happy.)

134
00:03:59,040 --> 00:04:00,080
It was Woo Jin.

135
00:04:00,510 --> 00:04:01,649
(He forgets about the truth...)

136
00:04:01,650 --> 00:04:03,050
(and mistakenly remembers it as Min Hyun's doing.)

137
00:04:03,310 --> 00:04:05,520
(He succeeds in getting back at Min Hyun, the wrong target.)

138
00:04:05,650 --> 00:04:07,389
- Who am I supposed to pick? - Pick one.

139
00:04:07,390 --> 00:04:08,590
None of them...

140
00:04:08,750 --> 00:04:10,289
have kicked a ball.

141
00:04:10,290 --> 00:04:12,660
I wish I could pick our camera operator.

142
00:04:12,920 --> 00:04:15,059
Jae Hwan, I'm the youngest. That means I'm the fastest.

143
00:04:15,060 --> 00:04:17,829
Isn't Min Hyun good with his body since he is an action star?

144
00:04:17,830 --> 00:04:19,499
Hasn't Ji Sung played jokgu in the military?

145
00:04:19,500 --> 00:04:20,729
Okay, I've made up my mind. Here I go.

146
00:04:20,730 --> 00:04:21,830
Whom will he pick?

147
00:04:23,200 --> 00:04:24,200
Seriously.

148
00:04:26,170 --> 00:04:27,869
- Are you serious? - Am I out?

149
00:04:27,870 --> 00:04:28,870
No, I pick you.

150
00:04:30,040 --> 00:04:33,909
(Team Jae Hwan's first member is Ji Sung!)

151
00:04:33,910 --> 00:04:35,079
This makes no sense.

152
00:04:35,080 --> 00:04:37,319
Why didn't you pick me?

153
00:04:37,320 --> 00:04:38,820
- Rock-paper-scissors. - For goodness' sake.

154
00:04:40,180 --> 00:04:41,189
Hey, hold on.

155
00:04:41,190 --> 00:04:42,819
The two of us should show us.

156
00:04:42,820 --> 00:04:43,889
The form?

157
00:04:43,890 --> 00:04:45,160
- Pass. - The form?

158
00:04:45,520 --> 00:04:46,520
Here.

159
00:04:46,521 --> 00:04:47,530
(How is my form?)

160
00:04:47,630 --> 00:04:48,989
Okay, I got it.

161
00:04:48,990 --> 00:04:49,990
Hey, Min Hyun.

162
00:04:51,730 --> 00:04:53,560
(Awkward)

163
00:04:53,730 --> 00:04:54,870
(Mr. Taekkyeon is back.)

164
00:04:55,030 --> 00:04:56,030
(Laughing)

165
00:04:56,170 --> 00:04:57,569
Why did you trap it with your chest?

166
00:04:57,570 --> 00:04:59,540
Don't you know the rules? Why did you touch it twice?

167
00:05:00,440 --> 00:05:02,709
- I pick Min Hyun. - Okay. That's good.

168
00:05:02,710 --> 00:05:04,480
See? I know how it's done.

169
00:05:05,210 --> 00:05:06,239
All right. Come here.

170
00:05:06,240 --> 00:05:08,049
I'm really good at sports. I'll do my best.

171
00:05:08,050 --> 00:05:09,050
- I'll teach you. - You never know.

172
00:05:09,051 --> 00:05:10,919
- I'll teach you. - What are the rules?

173
00:05:10,920 --> 00:05:11,920
What are the rules?

174
00:05:11,980 --> 00:05:12,980
(Oh, my)

175
00:05:12,981 --> 00:05:14,319
(I don't know where to begin.)

176
00:05:14,320 --> 00:05:16,619
Kick the ball and send it to the opposing team's section.

177
00:05:16,620 --> 00:05:17,690
- Okay. - You can do it.

178
00:05:18,020 --> 00:05:19,819
- Pick the vest color. - It's important.

179
00:05:19,820 --> 00:05:21,389
- Okay. Let's go with sky blue... - Okay.

180
00:05:21,390 --> 00:05:22,959
because they're a bit dark.

181
00:05:22,960 --> 00:05:24,059
Why are you calling me dark?

182
00:05:24,060 --> 00:05:25,329
I have a bright personality.

183
00:05:25,330 --> 00:05:27,070
- I'm an extrovert. - Orange is cooler.

184
00:05:27,570 --> 00:05:29,299
Guys, should I take off my shirt or not?

185
00:05:29,300 --> 00:05:30,300
(Acting tough)

186
00:05:30,301 --> 00:05:31,870
(It's rare to see Min Hyun makes a fuss.)

187
00:05:31,940 --> 00:05:33,499
- This is... - Why do you ask?

188
00:05:33,500 --> 00:05:34,869
- Do you feel hot? - Once I take it off,

189
00:05:34,870 --> 00:05:35,870
I'll go all out.

190
00:05:36,470 --> 00:05:38,539
- Keep it on for now. - Okay.

191
00:05:38,540 --> 00:05:40,079
I'll take it off if we're losing.

192
00:05:40,080 --> 00:05:41,080
Okay.

193
00:05:41,081 --> 00:05:42,950
(He seals his jokgu skills.)

194
00:05:43,210 --> 00:05:44,350
- Team Sonny's Sons. - Team Sonny's Sons.

195
00:05:45,020 --> 00:05:46,650
- We have the visuals. - We're Team Visuals.

196
00:05:46,980 --> 00:05:48,350
I wasn't going to do this.

197
00:05:48,620 --> 00:05:50,390
(Sung Woon suddenly takes off his socks.)

198
00:05:52,390 --> 00:05:53,660
What's this?

199
00:05:54,930 --> 00:05:57,230
(Sung Woon shows off his fancy footwork.)

200
00:05:57,600 --> 00:06:00,100
(Intimidating the opposing team)

201
00:06:00,870 --> 00:06:02,300
- What's going on? - My goodness.

202
00:06:02,600 --> 00:06:04,040
- Must you do that with your hands? - Yes.

203
00:06:04,470 --> 00:06:05,570
Why is he so excited?

204
00:06:05,740 --> 00:06:07,370
- Why is he so excited? - My goodness.

205
00:06:07,670 --> 00:06:09,839
He looks so cheeky.

206
00:06:09,840 --> 00:06:11,079
Are we supposed to go barefoot?

207
00:06:11,080 --> 00:06:12,180
(Oh, my)

208
00:06:12,340 --> 00:06:13,340
(At that moment,)

209
00:06:14,280 --> 00:06:16,080
(a van arrives at the vacation rental.)

210
00:06:16,210 --> 00:06:17,780
Hold on. I think someone is here.

211
00:06:17,850 --> 00:06:19,620
- They're here. - Hey.

212
00:06:20,050 --> 00:06:22,120
- Okay. - The ringers are here.

213
00:06:22,520 --> 00:06:23,759
(Hold on.)

214
00:06:23,760 --> 00:06:24,859
What's up with Seong Wu?

215
00:06:24,860 --> 00:06:26,520
What's up with Seong Wu?

216
00:06:26,860 --> 00:06:28,489
What did you guys do? I bet they slept.

217
00:06:28,490 --> 00:06:29,490
Their faces are puffy.

218
00:06:29,491 --> 00:06:31,960
Have you guys flown a plane?

219
00:06:32,430 --> 00:06:33,799
We flew a plane.

220
00:06:33,800 --> 00:06:35,069
- All right. - I'm serious.

221
00:06:35,070 --> 00:06:37,099
- I'm serious. We aren't lying. - This isn't the right time.

222
00:06:37,100 --> 00:06:38,100
You can tell us later.

223
00:06:38,101 --> 00:06:40,509
It's time to play jokgu. Do you want to die?

224
00:06:40,510 --> 00:06:42,169
- Do you want to die? - What?

225
00:06:42,170 --> 00:06:43,469
Jokgu, my foot.

226
00:06:43,470 --> 00:06:44,640
(It sounds like he is swearing.)

227
00:06:45,840 --> 00:06:46,979
(He can't believe his ears.)

228
00:06:46,980 --> 00:06:48,410
- "Jokgu, my foot." - Stop jokgu-ing around.

229
00:06:48,980 --> 00:06:50,849
Play rock-paper-scissors for Ji Hoon and Seong Wu.

230
00:06:50,850 --> 00:06:52,719
- Captains, rock-paper-scissors. - Scissors.

231
00:06:52,720 --> 00:06:53,720
- Rock-paper-scissors. - Scissors.

232
00:06:53,721 --> 00:06:54,890
(Sung Woon gets to choose.)

233
00:06:54,990 --> 00:06:56,489
Let's see your jokgu form.

234
00:06:56,490 --> 00:06:58,089
- Our jokgu form? - All right.

235
00:06:58,090 --> 00:06:59,090
Ji Hoon.

236
00:07:00,190 --> 00:07:01,760
(The winking cutie walks forward.)

237
00:07:01,790 --> 00:07:03,029
Okay.

238
00:07:03,030 --> 00:07:04,030
Take this.

239
00:07:04,031 --> 00:07:05,900
(This is my form.)

240
00:07:06,460 --> 00:07:08,300
(The winking cutie's flying kick!)

241
00:07:10,300 --> 00:07:11,500
(Relaxed)

242
00:07:11,800 --> 00:07:12,940
(Look at him.)

243
00:07:13,040 --> 00:07:14,339
Show us, Seong Wu.

244
00:07:14,340 --> 00:07:15,340
(Gritting his teeth)

245
00:07:15,470 --> 00:07:16,470
Seong Wu.

246
00:07:20,850 --> 00:07:23,050
(Playing Sepak Takraw)

247
00:07:24,320 --> 00:07:26,020
What did he kick just now?

248
00:07:26,220 --> 00:07:28,189
- Hey. - Didn't he do acrobatics?

249
00:07:28,190 --> 00:07:30,119
I've played jokgu with Seong Wu before.

250
00:07:30,120 --> 00:07:31,259
- Right? - Yes.

251
00:07:31,260 --> 00:07:32,789
- Really? - I'm not half bad.

252
00:07:32,790 --> 00:07:34,129
Whom will Sung Woon pick?

253
00:07:34,130 --> 00:07:36,159
- Ji Hoon. - Come on!

254
00:07:36,160 --> 00:07:37,399
(Surprisingly, he picks Ji Hoon instead of Seong Wu!)

255
00:07:37,400 --> 00:07:38,400
- Come on! - I've played with Seong Wu.

256
00:07:38,400 --> 00:07:39,400
I've played with Seong Wu.

257
00:07:39,830 --> 00:07:41,669
- It's okay, Seong Wu. - This team isn't bad.

258
00:07:41,670 --> 00:07:43,370
