00:32:57,250 --> 00:32:59,049
(Avoiding eye contact)

1053
00:32:59,050 --> 00:33:02,090
I felt like Seong Wu was watching me.

1054
00:33:02,450 --> 00:33:03,620
(Fidgeting nervously)

1055
00:33:03,790 --> 00:33:06,959
I was very afraid about the errand...

1056
00:33:06,960 --> 00:33:09,690
they'd ask me to do.

1057
00:33:09,990 --> 00:33:11,829
I found it interesting.

1058
00:33:11,830 --> 00:33:13,560
I was like, "Bring it on."

1059
00:33:14,130 --> 00:33:15,299
(Whom will Seong Wu pick?)

1060
00:33:15,300 --> 00:33:16,500
(Min Hyun versus Jae Hwan versus Woo Jin)

1061
00:33:18,900 --> 00:33:20,070
Will Seong Wu use his superpower?

1062
00:33:21,000 --> 00:33:22,409
Jae Hwan.

1063
00:33:22,410 --> 00:33:24,710
(Ong's carer, Kim Jae Hwan)

1064
00:33:24,910 --> 00:33:26,380
(Thank goodness.)

1065
00:33:26,510 --> 00:33:28,510
- He hoped it wouldn't be him. - Why me?

1066
00:33:28,610 --> 00:33:30,109
It's a good thing. I won't ask you to do something hard.

1067
00:33:30,110 --> 00:33:31,579
- Really? - We used...

1068
00:33:31,580 --> 00:33:34,620
a portion of 1,000 dollars at a convenience store...

1069
00:33:34,880 --> 00:33:36,750
on snacks we can enjoy together.

1070
00:33:37,250 --> 00:33:40,489
We bought liquor and ice cups.

1071
00:33:40,490 --> 00:33:42,560
- Shall I set them up? - I'd like a drink.

1072
00:33:42,590 --> 00:33:44,959
Please pour out the drinks and give them to the members.

1073
00:33:44,960 --> 00:33:46,029
One cup each?

1074
00:33:46,030 --> 00:33:47,529
Yes, please do that.

1075
00:33:47,530 --> 00:33:49,069
- Shall I do it with him? - Yes.

1076
00:33:49,070 --> 00:33:50,599
Set things up, Min Hyun.

1077
00:33:50,600 --> 00:33:52,029
Are you asking me to do it?

1078
00:33:52,030 --> 00:33:54,669
- Yes. Min Hyun, go and help him. - Okay.

1079
00:33:54,670 --> 00:33:56,210
I think that'll be nice.

1080
00:33:56,670 --> 00:33:57,769
Let's have a sip each.

1081
00:33:57,770 --> 00:33:59,840
(Jirung's carer, Hwang Min Hyun)

1082
00:34:00,380 --> 00:34:01,709
(The two carers set things up quickly...)

1083
00:34:01,710 --> 00:34:03,080
(so that they can't change their minds.)

1084
00:34:03,510 --> 00:34:06,080
(Carer Jjaeni prepares the ice cups.)

1085
00:34:06,580 --> 00:34:09,190
(Carer Hwang pours the drink.)

1086
00:34:10,520 --> 00:34:12,089
There is no soft drink.

1087
00:34:12,090 --> 00:34:13,789
- There is no soft drink. - Do you want it as it is?

1088
00:34:13,790 --> 00:34:15,590
We didn't buy it. It looks good.

1089
00:34:16,260 --> 00:34:17,959
I've done this at a part-time job.

1090
00:34:17,960 --> 00:34:19,029
You can hold the cups like this.

1091
00:34:19,030 --> 00:34:20,260
You won't drink, will you?

1092
00:34:21,000 --> 00:34:22,000
Here you go.

1093
00:34:22,001 --> 00:34:24,069
Sung Woon and Ji Sung.

1094
00:34:24,070 --> 00:34:26,139
- Ji Sung, take a drink. - Okay.

1095
00:34:26,140 --> 00:34:27,299
- After that... - Thank you.

1096
00:34:27,300 --> 00:34:29,040
- Jin Young, take a drink. - All right.

1097
00:34:29,270 --> 00:34:30,539
- It's good. - Seong Wu,

1098
00:34:30,540 --> 00:34:32,439
tell me if you need anything.

1099
00:34:32,440 --> 00:34:33,580
- Okay. - All right.

1100
00:34:33,740 --> 00:34:36,449
How were the Wanna List items Wannable requested?

1101
00:34:36,450 --> 00:34:39,650
I wanted to try a team shooting sport.

1102
00:34:39,980 --> 00:34:40,980
I had fun.

1103
00:34:43,220 --> 00:34:45,859
When you look at the results,

1104
00:34:45,860 --> 00:34:47,619
I haven't given an outstanding performance.

1105
00:34:47,620 --> 00:34:48,659
However,

1106
00:34:48,660 --> 00:34:50,329
when I shot the rifle...

1107
00:34:50,330 --> 00:34:53,630
and the opponents got hit...

1108
00:34:53,930 --> 00:34:57,129
and went back to their base, I became excited...

1109
00:34:57,130 --> 00:34:58,670
while looking at their backs.

1110
00:34:59,000 --> 00:35:01,940
Thanks to Wannable, I made a fun memory with the members.

1111
00:35:03,070 --> 00:35:04,510
I was so thankful.

1112
00:35:04,910 --> 00:35:06,179
I was very happy.

1113
00:35:06,180 --> 00:35:08,210
I didn't have any distracting thoughts.

1114
00:35:09,180 --> 00:35:13,520
(Thanks to Wannable's request, Ji Hoon flew.)

1115
00:35:14,320 --> 00:35:15,590
(True happiness)

1116
00:35:16,190 --> 00:35:20,060
It's a memory I won't forget even after many years.

1117
00:35:20,460 --> 00:35:24,060
I kept smiling. I was smiling from ear to ear.

1118
00:35:24,660 --> 00:35:27,230
(Ong Dance of happiness)

1119
00:35:27,430 --> 00:35:28,459
The thing is,

1120
00:35:28,460 --> 00:35:31,870
we have a fun and happy time when we're by ourselves.

1121
00:35:32,840 --> 00:35:36,970
(Wanna One's day was full of the Wanna List items.)

1122
00:35:37,140 --> 00:35:40,810
More diverse and fulfilling activities filled...

1123
00:35:41,640 --> 00:35:43,850
our day today.

1124
00:35:44,180 --> 00:35:48,379
I hope people who filled out the Wanna List...

1125
00:35:48,380 --> 00:35:51,390
will work less and earn more money.

1126
00:35:53,460 --> 00:35:56,789
I thought a lot about Wannable.

1127
00:35:56,790 --> 00:35:58,030
It was very fun.

1128
00:35:59,760 --> 00:36:02,330
I hope today won't be the end.

1129
00:36:03,130 --> 00:36:07,669
I hope I'll continue to have...

1130
00:36:07,670 --> 00:36:10,609
such thankful occasions with the members.

1131
00:36:10,610 --> 00:36:11,669
I had that thought.

1132
00:36:11,670 --> 00:36:13,879
While filming,

1133
00:36:13,880 --> 00:36:16,809
I kept dreaming of the future.

1134
00:36:16,810 --> 00:36:17,980
(He dreamed the future with Wanna One and Wannable.)

1135
00:36:24,890 --> 00:36:28,790
(Their love for Wannable grows deeper on this special night.)

1136
00:36:29,460 --> 00:36:31,529
It doesn't have to be what happened today.

1137
00:36:31,530 --> 00:36:33,629
Share your thoughts on the shoot of "WANNA ONE GO..."

1138
00:36:33,630 --> 00:36:36,370
and your time at Wanna Base.

1139
00:36:37,200 --> 00:36:40,199
I felt reassured during the shoot.

1140
00:36:40,200 --> 00:36:41,200
Seriously.

1141
00:36:41,870 --> 00:36:45,239
Being able to relax during the shoot...

1142
00:36:45,240 --> 00:36:47,640
was reassuring in every way.

1143
00:36:49,610 --> 00:36:51,850
I thought, "Wanna One is Wanna One."

1144
00:36:53,350 --> 00:36:57,090
"Wanna One doesn't disappoint."

1145
00:36:58,390 --> 00:37:02,120
One member played with a gun.

1146
00:37:02,530 --> 00:37:04,130
One member ate.

1147
00:37:04,930 --> 00:37:08,099
One member sat on the sofa and watched the others.

1148
00:37:08,100 --> 00:37:09,700
(Nothing has changed!)

1149
00:37:10,600 --> 00:37:13,469
The scene from 7 to 8 years ago...

1150
00:37:13,470 --> 00:37:16,070
unfolded before my eyes.

1151
00:37:16,870 --> 00:37:18,570
Even after years,

1152
00:37:19,180 --> 00:37:21,409
coming together creates a synergy...

1153
00:37:21,410 --> 00:37:23,810
and unique vibes.

1154
00:37:24,950 --> 00:37:27,219
They're definitely impactful.

1155
00:37:27,220 --> 00:37:28,920
(They're definitely impactful.)

1156
00:37:29,150 --> 00:37:31,120
It was so nice.

1157
00:37:34,460 --> 00:37:36,159
I got excited...

1158
00:37:36,160 --> 00:37:37,829
- every time I came to Wanna Base. - That's right.

1159
00:37:37,830 --> 00:37:40,229
It felt a bit like home.

1160
00:37:40,230 --> 00:37:41,859
- It felt like my parents' place. - Yes.

1161
00:37:41,860 --> 00:37:45,269
Everyone forgot about going on a diet upon arrival.

1162
00:37:45,270 --> 00:37:47,269
- We always follow a strict diet. - Yes.

1163
00:37:47,270 --> 00:37:48,969
But at Wanna Base, we let things go.

1164
00:37:48,970 --> 00:37:50,140
- That's right. - I know.

1165
00:37:50,410 --> 00:37:53,639
It shows how comfortable we felt. During the shoot, right?

1166
00:37:53,640 --> 00:37:55,510
I didn't eat to be funny.

1167
00:37:55,980 --> 00:37:58,810
I just found myself reaching for more food.

1168
00:37:59,180 --> 00:38:00,779
Who knew I could eat so much?

1169
00:38:00,780 --> 00:38:02,020
(He ate with gusto until the end.)

1170
00:38:02,250 --> 00:38:03,549
I only found out this time.

1171
00:38:03,550 --> 00:38:04,620
(He learned about his appetite at Wanna Base.)

1172
00:38:04,890 --> 00:38:06,820
(Laughing)

1173
00:38:07,520 --> 00:38:08,859
In any case,

1174
00:38:08,860 --> 00:38:12,260
we're always in front of the cameras.

1175
00:38:13,660 --> 00:38:16,469
These days, I've been thinking hard...

1176
00:38:16,470 --> 00:38:20,440
about innocence.

1177
00:38:22,440 --> 00:38:26,410
What can I do to be as innocent as I was back then?

1178
00:38:27,510 --> 00:38:30,549
I want to show my instant reaction like I did...

1179
00:38:30,550 --> 00:38:32,079
in my younger days.

1180
00:38:32,080 --> 00:38:33,449
But when there is one input,

1181
00:38:33,450 --> 00:38:35,820
I have many different thoughts about it.

1182
00:38:36,890 --> 00:38:38,690
When I watch old videos of me,

1183
00:38:39,060 --> 00:38:43,829
I can see that I had innocence in my heart...

1184
00:38:43,830 --> 00:38:45,900
as I worked.

1185
00:38:46,300 --> 00:38:48,360
With pure emotions,

1186
00:38:49,530 --> 00:38:54,370
I'll be a Wanna One member who can show...

1187
00:38:54,740 --> 00:38:57,309
his good side.

1188
00:38:57,310 --> 00:38:59,440
(At the age of 28, Ji Hoon saw the answer in his 19-year-old self.)

1189
00:38:59,840 --> 00:39:01,839
When I see myself on the show,

1190
00:39:01,840 --> 00:39:05,410
I feel like that's who I really am.

1191
00:39:05,920 --> 00:39:07,750
I had that thought.

1192
00:39:08,320 --> 00:39:12,490
I think I've gone back to being a person named Park Ji Hoon.

1193
00:39:12,860 --> 00:39:14,020
Yes. I...

1194
00:39:14,790 --> 00:39:17,630
didn't care about the cameras at all.

1195
00:39:18,460 --> 00:39:20,299
I went back to my childhood innocence...

1196
00:39:20,300 --> 00:39:22,970
and enjoyed the happy moments without any distracting thoughts.

1197
00:39:24,270 --> 00:39:28,340
I thought like, "I've missed it a lot."

1198
00:39:29,540 --> 00:39:31,210
"Things used to be like this."

1199
00:39:36,750 --> 00:39:38,449
When you work,

1200
00:39:38,450 --> 00:39:41,580
you need to read the room on the set.

1201
00:39:41,980 --> 00:39:43,349
If there are seniors,

1202
00:39:43,350 --> 00:39:46,290
you need to take care of them.

1203
00:39:46,760 --> 00:39:48,419
- But you looked relaxed. - Yes. Very relaxed.

1204
00:39:48,420 --> 00:39:50,730
Yes. It was nice. Everyone looked relaxed.

1205
00:39:51,060 --> 00:39:52,289
There was a really funny moment.

1206
00:39:52,290 --> 00:39:55,330
Ji Hoon aimed a toy gun at me.

1207
00:39:56,130 --> 00:39:57,930
(He asked Ji Hoon to play with him.)

1208
00:39:58,470 --> 00:40:01,400
(Ji Hoon retaliated as if it were the natural course of events.)

1209
00:40:01,640 --> 00:40:03,970
It was so funny that I laughed for 30 minutes.

1210
00:40:04,140 --> 00:40:07,340
Even though it was funny, a part of me realized...

1211
00:40:07,810 --> 00:40:11,610
that I hadn't seen this side of him in a long while.

1212
00:40:11,810 --> 00:40:13,550
It brought back memories.

1213
00:40:16,390 --> 00:40:18,419
Woo Jin, do you think the sweet potatoes are done?

1214
00:40:18,420 --> 00:40:20,260
(Ruining the heartwarming moment)

1215
00:40:20,690 --> 00:40:22,160
Shall I take one out?

1216
00:40:22,590 --> 00:40:24,760
- In this atmosphere? - Back then...

1217
00:40:25,560 --> 00:40:29,300
(The sweet potato fanatic gets up in the end.)

1218
00:40:29,430 --> 00:40:32,970
(He can't stop eating until the very end.)

1219
00:40:33,270 --> 00:40:34,400
(Putting on the gloves)

1220
00:40:35,570 --> 00:40:36,670
(Picking up tongs)

1221
00:40:38,010 --> 00:40:40,580
(I'm so excited about the sweet potatoes.)

1222
00:40:40,940 --> 00:40:43,109
- I felt like I wasn't alone. - Right.

1223
00:40:43,110 --> 00:40:44,209
I...

1224
00:40:44,210 --> 00:40:45,450
(When you're exhausted)

1225
00:40:47,750 --> 00:40:52,320
(Wanna One members, I'll take out the sweet potatoes.)

1226
00:40:54,420 --> 00:40:56,960
(What's wrong with Min Hyun?)

1227
00:40:57,060 --> 00:40:58,589
(They end up watching Min Hyun take out the sweet potatoes.)

1228
00:40:58,590 --> 00:40:59,759
What are you doing?

1229
00:40:59,760 --> 00:41:00,859
He looks like a farm boy.

1230
00:41:00,860 --> 00:41:04,600
He wouldn't show that side anywhere else.

1231
00:41:04,630 --> 00:41:06,339
We joke that Wanna One is our personal color.

1232
00:41:06,340 --> 00:41:07,369
Right.

1233
00:41:07,370 --> 00:41:09,339
- Compared to our solo works, - They're different.

1234
00:41:09,340 --> 00:41:10,440
our group works are very different.

1235
00:41:11,210 --> 00:41:13,409
- Is it cooked? - Look.

1236
00:41:13,410 --> 00:41:14,910
(Min Hyun's personal color is a roasted sweet potato.)

1237
00:41:20,220 --> 00:41:22,079
It needs to be roasted for a long time.

1238
00:41:22,080 --> 00:41:23,219
(Why is this sweet potato stretchy?)

1239
00:41:23,220 --> 00:41:25,859
Is it normal for a sweet potato to stretch like that?

1240
00:41:25,860 --> 00:41:27,459
- Is it jelly? - Isn't it fully cooked?

1241
00:41:27,460 --> 00:41:29,560
- Min Hyun, is it a banana? - Isn't it fully cooked?

1242
00:41:29,960 --> 00:41:31,559
(Sweet potato, don't listen to them.)

1243
00:41:31,560 --> 00:41:33,460
- Keep talking. - It's like an eel.

1244
00:41:36,930 --> 00:41:38,729
(The roasted sweet potato is fully cooked.)

1245
00:41:38,730 --> 00:41:41,500
(Steamy)

1246
00:41:42,470 --> 00:41:44,069
(Wanna One members, look at this sweet potato.)

1247
00:41:44,070 --> 00:41:45,139
It's a roasted sweet potato.

1248
00:41:45,140 --> 00:41:46,710
(That's incredible.)

1249
00:41:47,040 --> 00:41:49,250
It's cooked. I didn't think it'd be cooked.

1250
00:41:49,550 --> 00:41:51,480
It's fully cooked. Eat as you talk.

1251
00:41:52,010 --> 00:41:54,219
(They finally begin eating the roasted sweet potato!)

1252
00:41:54,220 --> 00:41:55,220
Do you want me to peel it?

1253
00:41:55,221 --> 00:41:56,250
It's okay.

1254
00:41:56,920 --> 00:41:58,549
(Blowing)

1255
00:41:58,550 --> 00:42:00,260
(Blowing)

1256
00:42:00,960 --> 00:42:02,389
(He finally takes a bite.)

1257
00:42:02,390 --> 00:42:03,660
(Impressed)

1258
00:42:03,760 --> 00:42:04,860
- Isn't it tasty? - Yes.

1259
00:42:05,430 --> 00:42:07,730
(Bae Bae, try it.)

1260
00:42:08,530 --> 00:42:09,530
It's hot.

1261
00:42:09,530 --> 00:42:10,530
(He takes a bite thanks to Min Hyun.)

1262
00:42:11,600 --> 00:42:12,600
Isn't it hot?

1263
00:42:12,900 --> 00:42:13,970
Is it too hot?

1264
00:42:16,440 --> 00:42:18,970
(I see that it was too hot.)

1265
00:42:19,040 --> 00:42:21,439
(Bae Bae burns the roof of his mouth for trusting Min Hyun.)

1266
00:42:21,440 --> 00:42:23,310
- I'm sorry. - Try it too.

1267
00:42:27,880 --> 00:42:30,390
(They share their pain and make it twice as big.)

1268
00:42:30,820 --> 00:42:32,219
(While they're struggling with the sweet potato,)

1269
00:42:32,220 --> 00:42:33,620
(Jae Hwan is doing something?)

1270
00:42:33,760 --> 00:42:35,059
He really is a musical genius.

1271
00:42:35,060 --> 00:42:37,130
(He opens his guitar case.)

1272
00:42:38,490 --> 00:42:42,460
(Jae Hwan hummed "Again, Spring Breeze" in the van.)

1273
00:42:42,770 --> 00:42:44,670
Jae Hwan, you should sing live.

1274
00:42:45,030 --> 00:42:46,200
- We should do it. - Yes.

1275
00:42:46,900 --> 00:42:48,599
(Wanna One will have their group live singing...)

1276
00:42:48,600 --> 00:42:49,670
(after 7 years during the campfire.)

1277
00:42:50,210 --> 00:42:53,640
(The members practice for the live performance.)

1278
00:42:54,440 --> 00:42:56,380
(Bae Bae practices with a sweet potato.)

1279
00:42:56,710 --> 00:42:59,580
(Is the composer, Sung Woon, practicing with seriousness?)

1280
00:43:02,750 --> 00:43:05,960
(Cackling)

1281
00:43:06,260 --> 00:43:07,389
(The composer becomes very flustered.)

1282
00:43:07,390 --> 00:43:08,959
He'll redo it.

1283
00:43:08,960 --> 00:43:10,329
His throat isn't warmed up.

1284
00:43:10,330 --> 00:43:11,689
- It isn't like that. - It's his own song.

1285
00:43:11,690 --> 00:43:13,459
- My voice is gone. - Yes.

1286
00:43:13,460 --> 00:43:15,159
It was my first time hearing Sung Woon sing off-tune.

1287
00:43:15,160 --> 00:43:16,799
It's because he has talked too much.

1288
00:43:16,800 --> 00:43:19,539
Hey!

1289
00:43:19,540 --> 00:43:20,540
(I can't do it either.)

1290
00:43:21,170 --> 00:43:23,740
(Urgent mission: Warm up the throat!)

1291
00:43:24,540 --> 00:43:27,209
(Practicing diligently)

1292
00:43:27,210 --> 00:43:28,210
(This is our first live performance of the fan song.)

1293
00:43:29,550 --> 00:43:31,880
(Seong Wu's desperate battle makes everyone laugh.)

1294
00:43:32,050 --> 00:43:33,320
(Laughing)

1295
00:43:33,450 --> 00:43:35,550
This is Wanna One-core too.

1296
00:43:35,680 --> 00:43:37,449
This is Wanna One-core.

1297
00:43:37,450 --> 00:43:39,049
- We're good at singing live. - Yes.

1298
00:43:39,050 --> 00:43:40,659
- But we chatted all day long. - That's right.

1299
00:43:40,660 --> 00:43:43,359
- Seong Wu talked too much. - Right.

1300
00:43:43,360 --> 00:43:45,360
Would you give me a chance?

1301
00:43:45,730 --> 00:43:48,000
(Practicing again)

1302
00:43:51,200 --> 00:43:53,099
(He fails again.)

1303
00:43:53,100 --> 00:43:54,800
(Laughing)

1304
00:43:55,300 --> 00:43:56,910
(Jjaeni can't stop laughing.)

1305
00:44:00,480 --> 00:44:03,410
(Deity of singing, why do you put me through this trial?)

1306
00:44:03,550 --> 00:44:05,949
You said, "Wanna be the one" too many times.

1307
00:44:05,950 --> 00:44:07,350
- I know. - Wanna...

1308
00:44:07,480 --> 00:44:08,919
Wanna be the one!

1309
00:44:08,920 --> 00:44:10,249
(Deity of "Wanna be the one," please give me strength.)

1310
00:44:10,250 --> 00:44:11,590
(Wanna be the one!)

1311
00:44:12,120 --> 00:44:14,320
(Will his prayer be answered?)

1312
00:44:14,560 --> 00:44:16,459
(Impressed)

1313
00:44:16,460 --> 00:44:17,959
That part is ready. Let's begin.

1314
00:44:17,960 --> 00:44:19,400
The result can be autotuned.

1315
00:44:19,500 --> 00:44:20,729
(That can't be done.)

1316
00:44:20,730 --> 00:44:22,159
I don't know if it's possible.

1317
00:44:22,160 --> 00:44:23,330
- Let's begin. - Okay.

1318
00:44:24,470 --> 00:44:27,440
(Acoustic version of "Again, Spring Breeze" by Jjaeni)

1319
00:44:34,210 --> 00:44:35,240
Hey!

1320
00:44:36,580 --> 00:44:38,309
Hey! Make some noise!

1321
00:44:38,310 --> 00:44:39,580
(Wanna One, let's go!)

1322
00:44:43,950 --> 00:44:44,950
Come on!

1323
00:45:37,010 --> 00:45:38,570
One, two, three.

1324
00:45:51,550 --> 00:45:55,620
No one imagined that we'd meet again like this.

1325
00:45:56,090 --> 00:45:57,329
(We'll say hello. In 2, 3!)

1326
00:45:57,330 --> 00:46:00,729
(All I wanna do! Wanna One! Hello, we're Wanna One!)

1327
00:46:00,730 --> 00:46:05,700
We could gather around at Sangam on April 6...

1328
00:46:06,400 --> 00:46:09,139
because Wannable waited for us...

1329
00:46:09,140 --> 00:46:10,970
without forgetting about us.

1330
00:46:11,740 --> 00:46:13,339
I was so thankful.

1331
00:46:13,340 --> 00:46:18,350
The past memories flitted through my mind.

1332
00:46:19,950 --> 00:46:21,119
(An emotional reunion with Wannable felt like a spring dream.)

1333
00:46:21,120 --> 00:46:24,890
It was just like a dream.

1334
00:46:24,990 --> 00:46:26,120
(It's the same vending machine!)

1335
00:46:26,520 --> 00:46:29,360
(They became one again and headed to the door that was Wanna One.)

1336
00:46:29,690 --> 00:46:31,360
I felt a bit emotional back then.

1337
00:46:32,190 --> 00:46:33,800
I felt like I had come back as an adult.

1338
00:46:34,430 --> 00:46:35,630
Green light...

1339
00:46:36,470 --> 00:46:38,129
(Although they've grown up,)

1340
00:46:38,130 --> 00:46:41,370
(they become young when they're together.)

1341
00:46:41,600 --> 00:46:45,310
All of us went back to being children and ran around.

1342
00:46:46,180 --> 00:46:47,740
Wanna Base...

1343
00:46:48,640 --> 00:46:51,409
Although we didn't spend a long time there,

1344
00:46:51,410 --> 00:46:53,250
we became happy thanks to the place.

1345
00:46:56,150 --> 00:46:57,390
I love you.

1346
00:46:58,490 --> 00:46:59,490
Good night.

1347
00:46:59,491 --> 00:47:02,060
When I slept with the members under the same blanket,

1348
00:47:02,720 --> 00:47:07,460
I felt like I was sleeping with my allies.

1349
00:47:08,030 --> 00:47:11,529
I felt like I was sleeping with people...

1350
00:47:11,530 --> 00:47:13,470
I could really trust and depend on.

1351
00:47:14,200 --> 00:47:17,270
So I wasn't uncomfortable or worried in any way.

1352
00:47:18,270 --> 00:47:21,580
I still remember that feeling.

1353
00:47:22,540 --> 00:47:23,750
It was nice.

1354
00:47:25,110 --> 00:47:29,350
To Wanna One's precious time and precious days,

1355
00:47:30,320 --> 00:47:33,590
thank you for including me.

1356
00:47:34,660 --> 00:47:35,920
Everyone.

1357
00:47:36,790 --> 00:47:41,800
(The spring breeze blows again)

1358
00:47:42,300 --> 00:47:43,570
Is this a team dinner?

1359
00:47:45,900 --> 00:47:47,100
- One more time! - Together!

1360
00:47:49,440 --> 00:47:55,240
(The spring breeze that has returned makes them smile brightly.)

1361
00:47:58,550 --> 00:47:59,979
(The acoustic live performance of "Again, Spring Breeze" ends.)

1362
00:47:59,980 --> 00:48:01,450
It was a sloppy live performance.

1363
00:48:02,350 --> 00:48:03,649
It's good because we had fun.

1364
00:48:03,650 --> 00:48:06,120
- Jae Hwan, thank you. - My goodness.

1365
00:48:06,960 --> 00:48:08,490
I was so happy.

1366
00:48:08,620 --> 00:48:11,090
I'll always wait for "WANNA ONE GO."

1367
00:48:14,360 --> 00:48:16,669
(We thank Wannable for watching "WANNA ONE GO...")

1368
00:48:16,670 --> 00:48:18,930
(with the spring breeze that has returned.)

1369
00:48:19,570 --> 00:48:21,170
Jin Young, say something.

1370
00:48:22,240 --> 00:48:24,340
Did you think it was over?

1371
00:48:25,940 --> 00:48:29,540
I'm here with a surprise notice instead of the Open Pick Voting.

1372
00:48:30,150 --> 00:48:31,679
Is this really the end of the show?

1373
00:48:31,680 --> 00:48:34,150
No way! It isn't done yet!

1374
00:48:35,750 --> 00:48:38,050
Thus, we prepared a special episode of "WANNA ONE GO."

1375
00:48:38,350 --> 00:48:40,959
The last episode viewing with Wannable...

1376
00:48:40,960 --> 00:48:43,860
and that one game Wannable has been waiting for...

1377
00:48:44,090 --> 00:48:45,930
will be revealed.

1378
00:48:46,700 --> 00:48:50,830
Let's meet again on Mnet Plus at 6pm, June 16.

1379
00:48:50,970 --> 00:48:52,100
We'll be waiting.
